Class: Composer

Composer(uri, errorExpected)

A class that handles all of the interactions with a business network for
a currently executing Cucumber scenario and steps.

Constructor

new Composer(uri, errorExpected)

Constructor.

Parameters:
Name Type Description
uri string

The URI of the currently executing Cucumber scenario.
errorExpected boolean

Is an error expected in this Cucumber scenario?
